dc_description_s: Map shows at a scale of 1inch = 200 feet the Cooper Creek from State Street to past Federal Street in Camden. Also shows the area along the Delaware River from the City of Camden to the Camden/Burlington line. |Map shows owners of land and the land granted and leased. The map also shows Philadelphia, Pettys Island, the Delaware River, Camden, Pavonia, and Coopers Creek. Map includes a subsketch of 17th street between Stevens Street and the Delaware River
